DCPU
Robert Dionne
2012.03.30

I'm implementing Notch's DCPU.

DCPU specification: http://0x10c.com/highnerd/dcpu16_1_3.txt
Backup: https://github.com/robertsdionne/dcpu/blob/master/documentation/dcpu16_1_3.txt

Clock specification: http://dcpu.com/highnerd/rc_1/clock.txt
Backup: https://github.com/robertsdionne/dcpu/blob/master/documentation/clock.txt

LEM1802 specification: http://dcpu.com/highnerd/lem1802.txt
Backup: https://github.com/robertsdionne/dcpu/blob/master/documentation/lem1802.txt

Keyboard specification: http://dcpu.com/highnerd/rc_1/keyboard.txt
Backup: https://github.com/robertsdionne/dcpu/blob/master/documentation/keyboard.txt

To build:
1) Install libncurses-dev if needed.
2) Run ./waf configure
3) Then ./waf build run
